0.text: Bug 6657  Project rename error message has a strange chars in the front.

1.text: Found in V1.0 (R10 driver), and re-tested on v2.0  (Build 20011204).

4.text: STEPS:  Create a simple project called Simple1.

5.text: Create a simple project called Simple2 In the resource perspective, rename Simple1 to Simple 2 from the  Navigator.

6.text: RESULTS: You will see the message     "P/Simple2 exists.

8.text: EXPECTED RESULTS: See the message     "Simple2 exists.

10.text: without the P/ in the front.

11.text: NOTE: This does not happen in the Java Perspective (it brings up a dialog  instead of allowing renaming in-line).
